translate spanish strings:

    # game/MelanieKit.rpy:652
    old "{b}An API/content-incompatible version of the R18 patch is mounted!{/b}\n\n%s %s requires a minimum R18 patch version of %s, but you have version %s mounted.\n\nPlease download a compatible version of the R18 patch from {a=https://vnstudioelan.itch.io/heart-of-the-woods-r18-patch}itch.io{/a}.\n\nFor detailed information on how to apply patches and mods, please {a=openREADME://}refer to the README{/a}.\n{b}You can also simply {a=openGameDataRootDirectory://}{b}click here{/b}{/a} to open your \"game/\" folder.{/b}\n\n{font=gui/fonts/SourceHanSans-Regular.otf}※{/font} If you previously copied an \"images/\" folder to your \"game/\" folder as part of an older patch, please remove it. Third-party mod assets can be left alone, if you have any installed.\n\n{font=gui/fonts/SourceHanSans-Regular.otf}※{/font} This alert will show at every launch until the R18 patch is either updated or removed.\n\nContinue with the all-ages version of %s?"
    new "{b}An API/content-incompatible version of the R18 patch is mounted!{/b}\n\n%s %s requires a minimum R18 patch version of %s, but you have version %s mounted.\n\nPlease download a compatible version of the R18 patch from {a=https://vnstudioelan.itch.io/heart-of-the-woods-r18-patch}itch.io{/a}.\n\nFor detailed information on how to apply patches and mods, please {a=openREADME://}refer to the README{/a}.\n{b}You can also simply {a=openGameDataRootDirectory://}{b}click here{/b}{/a} to open your \"game/\" folder.{/b}\n\n{font=gui/fonts/SourceHanSans-Regular.otf}※{/font} If you previously copied an \"images/\" folder to your \"game/\" folder as part of an older patch, please remove it. Third-party mod assets can be left alone, if you have any installed.\n\n{font=gui/fonts/SourceHanSans-Regular.otf}※{/font} This alert will show at every launch until the R18 patch is either updated or removed.\n\nContinue with the all-ages version of %s?"

